**Advance tax** is income tax paid in quarterly instalments during the financial year, rather than as a lump sum at year-end. If your total tax liability exceeds ₹10,000, you must pay advance tax in 4 instalments: 15% by June 15, 45% by September 15, 75% by December 15, and 100% by March 15.
